{"tid":384122,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇m男巴打間唔中會FF自己比TB調教？","createTime":"2017-09-02T05:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T08:50:19.000Z","uid":68626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c00cd3d5d6dc2016c5cbe2c65f20ae6c8daed4","tid":384122,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:25:56.000Z","msg":"d大隻TB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時會唔會間唔中FF自己<br />\n比佢地禁住黎打反抗唔到<br />\n比佢地鬧點解連女人都打唔贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7799a449591317126e92b8663f2c51b3c10dc44d","tid":384122,"uid":27558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:27:08.000Z","msg":"含啦臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab15ac53a3e05e4d3ddfaa13ca443d2b711d0ef","tid":384122,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"801f2df073ea0470a47c0b087aac955c70508d88","tid":384122,"uid":135986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:48:37.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"f380a6b490d0a37e6bd56f09777957c9394a6329","tid":384122,"uid":27320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:50:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}